Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Shinichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a famous high school detective\Nwho's solved countless cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I solved a roller coaster murder\Ncase with no difficulty at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then a mysterious organization\Nforced me to take a strange poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things looked really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! What's going to happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kidnapping of the Company\NPresident's Daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, little boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're these guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a 2nd year high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get that\Ncut on your head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man dressed in black hit me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found an injured boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's a grade school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's a grade school student?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These officers are acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There may have been an incident--\Nhe's received injuries to his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may have a crime on\Nour hands! Try to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:35.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're back, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dad, can't you stop\Nthrowing trash all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you don't get any jobs!\NAnd why Mom ran out on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose what jobs I take.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where's that so-called\Ndetective of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was before we left\Nthe amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ran! You go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could Shinichi be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't run that far,\Nso why am I so out of breath?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've shrunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use this.\NOur organization's latest poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because\NI swallowed that pill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Shinichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm away at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're interested in hiring me,\Nplease leave your name and number...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. He's still not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably out havin' dinner\Nwith his novelist dad or somethin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi's parents moved\Nto America three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he's living all by himself now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something must've\Nhappened to him afterward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop by his house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What about my dinner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! Can't I even get\Ninto my own house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A relative of Shinichi, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His house is the next one over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Hiroshi Agasa\Nand you're 52!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an eccentric inventor\Nand claim that you're a genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but everything you make is junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also have a mole on your butt\Nthat has a hair sticking out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Shinichi knows about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been spreading my\Nsecrets around, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's because I'm Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was forced to take some weird pill\Nwhich made my body shrink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pill that shrunk you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I highly doubt any such pills exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You suspicious little punk!\NI'm taking you to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor! You tripped while hurrying
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on your way back from the\NColombo restaurant, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your clothes, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The front of your clothes are still wet,\Nyet the back is completely dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's evidence that you\Nwere running in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, you also\Nhave mud on your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only street in this area\Nwhere you could get mud on you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is in front of Colombo,\Nwhich is under construction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus some of Colombo's special\Nmeat sauce is still in your mustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary, my dear Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the uncompleted poison mysteriously\Ncaused your body to shrink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lame. My clothes from\Nwhen I was a kid fit perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, Professor!\NYou are a genius, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me some medicine that'll\Nchange me back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on there! I don't even know\Nthe ingredients of the pill you took...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all we need to do is\Nfigure out where those guys are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get some of those pills!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that would certainly help...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they find out you're still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll come back to put\Nan end to you for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this must stay a secret\Nbetween just the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't tell anyone at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means not even Ran-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi! Are you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Hide quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're home, then you can\Nat least answer the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Professor Agasa?\NWhere's Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disguise time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, these are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is there someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be really shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, face this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He belongs to a distant\Nrelative of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My name's Shin-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan? That's an odd name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad was a big fan\Nof Conan Doyle, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me of Shinichi somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ran-kun, I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could let him\Nstay at your house for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His parents are in the hospital\Nafter getting into an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They asked me to look after him,\Nbut I live a bachelor's life, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but I'll have to ask my dad first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! So, you're willing to take him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great news, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if Ran finds out\Nwho I really am while I'm there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first step to turning\Nyou back to normal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is finding the men in black\Nwho used that drug on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ran-kun's house\Nis a detective agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her dad might run across\Ninformation about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Conan-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never get used to this name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a girl at school or someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I really like, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's that Shinichi boy\Nyou were looking for earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been kind of\Na tease since he was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's always been so full of himself\Nand a big mystery geek,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:09:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's also courageous,\Ncool, and dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like Shinichi a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But keep this a secret from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are! This is my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like I've gained\Na cute little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I can talk to you\Nabout anything, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you to my dad!\NFollow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one! I got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first job in 6 months!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone kidnapped\Na rich guy's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some guy dressed in black!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man dressed in black?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This case is calling my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling for the famous detective\Nknown as Kogoro Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he got in before\NI could stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm riding in a car! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He belongs to a relative\Nof Professor Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you bothering\Nme while I work! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get out!\NWe're on a freeway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person kidnapped\Nwas my only daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko Tani. 10 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My butler Asao saw the\Nperpetrator with his own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, I can't see the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being so small is such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the surrounding situation\Nlike when she was kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just an acquaintance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Watch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Asao-san, please\Nexplain in detail what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It occurred when she went to play\Noutside after returning from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man dressed in black suddenly\Nappeared from a corner of the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give this message to her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he wants his daughter back,\Nhe'll shut down his company for 1 month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the police involved\Nand she's as good as dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon leaving those words,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the kidnapper scaled a pine\Ntree and escaped outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did this man have any\Nspecial characteristics?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes aren't what\Nthey used to be, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't get in the way\Nof my dad's work, Conan-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone else hear the kidnapper's\Nvoice or any sounds out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Other than Asao-san's shouts\Nfor help, it was completely quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Asao-san was the\Nonly one who saw the perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the demands, the kidnapper\Nis likely someone from a rival company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! To think they would\Nwant money on top of that demand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a phone call just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They demanded that I prepare\N300 million, all in used bills!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some sort of mistake, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! You will remain quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which companies stand to gain something\Nif your company shuts down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something not right\Nabout this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the perpetrator\Nkidnap her inside her home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been easier on\Nher way home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And being clearly seen is too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But demanding used bills\Nis oddly cautious...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're really good\Nat soccer, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi would do that whenever\Nhe was thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said it would get his mind working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shinichi is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rare it is for Jumbo to\Nbe friendly with a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper climbed this pine tree\Nto break in and to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means this dog\Nmust have barked at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I've figured this case out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like this dog barks\Nat all strangers, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Jumbo is one of the best\Nguard dogs around, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the servants said\Nthat it was completely quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for when\Nthe butler was yelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where are you going, Asao-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He realized it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something strange\Nabout your story!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper snuck in, took the girl,\Nand escaped using that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet the guard dog didn't bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus your testimony\Nis too full of ambiguity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there really a man\Ndressed in black, Asao-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or shall I say, Kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asao! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do this for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone put you up to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did this entirely of my own accord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where is the girl now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nearby hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Detective Kogoro Mori on the job,\Nno case goes unsolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still another side to this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! There's a phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy. Tell them to call back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the 300 million ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the guy who kidnapped\Nyour daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!\NThe kidnapper has already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you did have help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did it alone! Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being kidnapped\Nfor the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was most likely kidnapped\Nagain by someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By someone much worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an impatient man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get the 300 million ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or there's no telling what'll\Nhappen to your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'll get the money somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give Akiko back unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep him talking and try\Nto find out his location!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His location?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy! I'm in a storeroom of a school!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see a big chimney\Nfrom the window-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call again in one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the money ready by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big-mouthed brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big chimney visible\Nfrom a school storeroom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't enough information to\Npinpoint which school it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, please buy us some\Ntime by preparing the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper's nervous now\Nthat we know his location!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't rescue\Nthe little girl soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been very long\Nsince she was kidnapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I figured they might\Nbe somewhere nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he could have\Ngotten far with a little girl with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we limit it to the nearby area,\Nthat leaves only so many schools to check!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! After that dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chimney she sees is probably\Neither a factory or a bathhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only 5 schools in the\Narea where you can see chimneys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! It wasn't any of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any other schools\Nthat have views of chimneys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must not be\Nin this area after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She saw this building from the\Nside and mistook it for a chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schools in this vicinity that\Nhave a side view of this building...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Futatsubashi Middle School!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Place the money on the\Nbench in Hyakujii Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I have it in my hands,\NI'll return the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear Akiko's voice\None more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have plenty of time\Nlater to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means your role\Nis just about over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I mean, Conan Edogawa. A detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mockin' me,\Nyou little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! I can't put any power\Ninto it with my body so small!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! My soccer kicks\Nhave weakened, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I do find the criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in my smaller body, I can't even\Ncapture them or beat them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playtime's over! Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed you and then I saw\NJumbo jump out from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're the one behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnapping case? Detective\NKogoro Mori is your man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who came up\Nwith the idea to kidnap me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy's always too busy\Nwith work to care about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I had Asao-san "kidnap" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could get Daddy\Nto spend time with me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if his company had to take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So, the first\Nkidnapping was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my daughter\Ndid ask for your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find it difficult to\Nforgive what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you realize this, Asao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As punishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will make arrangements for a\N1-week trip that starts tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trip to Australia, where\NAkiko has always wanted to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She and I will be going\Nthere together, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting the dog go so he could find\Nmy daughter was a stroke of genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's because of all\Nthe experience I've had!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you to talk?\NI was the one who found him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will express my gratitude\Nto you another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she means him, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Dad, about this boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Agasa asked if\Nwe would take care of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:22:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a job the instant he showed up,\Nand then I solved it like an ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just might be a\Ngod of good fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with us and become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:38.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:47.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:52.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:59.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:09.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:22.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:32.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:37.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just transferred here!\NMy name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go back to\Ngrade school again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.85,0:24:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.94,0:24:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Shinichi were here,\Nhe'd easily solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.43,0:24:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could that\Nmystery nerd have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-kun! You were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.83,0:24:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed my mind about you,\N"Great Detective"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.26,0:24:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do that. I could never\Nbe as strong as Yoko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.76,0:24:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.36,0:24:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Murder Behind the Locked Doors\Nof a Celebrity's Apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.21,0:24:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.72,0:24:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.42,0:25:54.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.44,0:24:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can beat me next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.56,0:24:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
